thread.title: BRIEF-Sea Harvest Group Posts FY HEPS 108.0 Cents

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Sea Harvest Group Posts FY HEPS 108.0 Cents
text:
March 6 (Reuters) - Sea Harvest Group Ltd:
* FY ‍HEADLINE EARNINGS PER SHARE 108.0 CENTS VERSUS 56.4 CENTS​
* ‍GROUP REVENUE FOR YEAR INCREASED BY 10% TO R2.1 BILLION​
* FY ‍EARNINGS PER SHARE 119.0 CENTS VERSUS 86.4​ CENTS YEAR AGO
* GROSS FULL AND FINAL CASH DIVIDEND AMOUNTING TO 31 CENTS PER SHARE, IN RESPECT OF YEAR ENDED 31 DECEMBER 2017, WAS DECLARED Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
